osvSchema.details: Cryptographic issue in HLOS as derived keys used to encrypt/decrypt information is present on stack after use.

description_data.value: Cryptographic issue in HLOS as derived keys used to encrypt/decrypt information is present on stack after use.

descriptions.value: Cryptographic issue in HLOS as derived keys used to encrypt/decrypt information is present on stack after use.
Problema criptográfico en HLOS ya que las claves derivadas utilizadas para cifrar/descifrar información están presentes en la pila después de su uso.
